item.title: Sponsorship Drive
item.description: Dear Visionaries, Innovators, and those linked to the land, I am excited to announce that we are gearing up for the 3rd Annual CyberTractor Challenge, set for June 10-14, 2024, near the dynamic campus of Iowa State University, and it’s that time where we must start on the process of finding sponsors!
